## Chat API sketch

### Request
```json
{
  "message": "Turn this still into a 2 second GIF with a blink, breath, and smug pause.",
  "attachments": ["img_ref_44"],
  "continuity_ref": "scene_prev",
  "output": "gif"
}
```

### Parsed command
```json
{
  "intent": "animate_still",
  "duration_sec": 2.0,
  "micro_motion": ["blink", "breath"],
  "expression_arc": ["neutral", "smug_pause"],
  "format": "gif"
}
```

### Response
```json
{
  "status": "ok",
  "preview_url": "...",
  "artifact_type": "gif",
  "scene_id": "scene_2026_04_09_a",
  "program_id": "prog_1042"
}
```

